                                                                    "description": "This pizza is a spicy sensation that will wake up your taste buds. It starts with a crispy crust, topped with a fiery sauce that packs a punch. The pizza is then loaded with sliced mushrooms, roasted garlic, and a mix of colorful peppers including jalapeno, red pepperica, and capsicum. Each bite is a delicious combination of spicy, smoky, and savory flavors, with a range of textures that will keep you coming back for more. If you love a little heat in your food, this pizza is sure to satisfy.",
